Empowering Sports Medicine
Healthy Roster is the only injury documentation tool that allows athletic trainers to build deeper relationships with parents and prove outreach works.


























































































































































 


Track injuries | engage parents | Validate DOWNSTREAM REVENUE | Prove Value







Healthy Roster is a platform built for Sports Medicine!At Healthy Roster we're empowering Sports Medicine departments to easily prove their immense value through end-to-end injury tracking and reporting. By providing AT's with a dramatically better mobile injury documentation and communication tool, and integrating Healthy Roster with your healthcare system's main EHR, we can help prove the value of outreach to your healthcare organization!Here's what you get with Healthy Roster:Mobile Injury Documentation - we make it easy for AT's to add, track and edit injuries on the go. Secure Communication - we enable AT's to securely text/chat and live video chat with everyone involved in the athlete's care (coaches, parents, primary care teams, and even other AT's and orthopedic team members). Research Level Reporting -  we provide sports medicine and orthopedic service line directors with dashboard access to real-time, system-wide injury data, in-depth AT activity reporting and complete patient care history. EHR Integration - connect Healthy Roster to your healthcare system's EHR (Epic, Cerner, AllScripts, NEXTGEN, AthenaHealth, and many more) we can give you powerful reporting you can use for downstream revenue validation.HEALTHY ROSTER DEMOTo see a quick online demo of how Healthy Roster works, please fill select a date and time below:


LEARN MOREIf you'd like more information about the Healthy Roster's Sports Medicine platform, please fill out the contact form below. We'll reply promptly to help answer any questions!





