Healthy Roster, Inc.

Healthy Roster connects parents of youth sports athletes with Certified Athletic Trainers from local area hospitals they know and trust. 






Stage

$500K in TTM Revenue



Industry

Healthcare Services



Location

Dublin, OH, US



Currency

USD



Founded

March 2015



Employees

6



Incorporation Type

C-corp



Website

healthyroster.com

















Company Summary





Healthy Roster connects parents of youth sports athletes with Certified Athletic Trainers from local area healthcare organizations they know and trust. Hospitals and Orthopedic Clinics use our software to provide schools, club teams and youth leagues with our Virtual Athletic Trainer mobile app. Our app enables the parents, coaches and Athletic Trainers to report, track and communicate about injuries for each athlete. 






















Team













Nathan Heerdt






































Loading



